# Code quality (CloneCV)

## Commands

- `npm run lint`
- `npm run test`
- `npm run format:check` (pre-merge recommended)
- `npm run build` (when touching routes, env, or Next config)

## Project checks

- Prefer surgical diffs; no drive-by refactors
- API: friendly errors; no raw stack traces to clients
- Service-role / admin: verify auth before privileged actions
- Chat: FAQ short-circuit before Gemini when possible; `/demo` must not persist
- Align with F-XX in `docs/02` / status in `docs/07` when changing product behavior

## Report format

Critical → Should-fix → Nit. Fix only when asked.
